The paper presents a type-based approach to programming and verifying MPI-like programs against protocols, which involves translating protocols into Why3, a deductive software verification tool. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Programming Languages (cs.PL), Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), or Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories.
